title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge.  Tot Gear Video - next week  Thanks to Chips Films for making a great video  http://chipsfilms.com/about/  Watch Charlie bit my finger: http://bit.ly/HDCYT_Charliebitme  T-Shirts http://charliebitme.firebrandstore.com/ iPhone  http://itunes.apple.com/gb/app/charlie-bit-me!!!/id494858348?mt=8 Android  https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.viralspiral.charlie  Twitter http://twitter.com/harryandcharlie

title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track. title: ACTION! Renault 5 Maxi Turbo: launch, flames & sound
description: Like me on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/davide458italia. My Blog: http://www.davide458italia.blogspot.it. Full HD video 1080p. Description: I filmed this awesome Renault 5 Maxi Turbo by AP Motorsport in action. title: Discover the New Renault ZOE
description: "Title: All Is Calm Artist: Whinnie Williams  Song: That's Entertainment Director: Carl Rinsch  ZOE integrates the most advanced electric technology. More than 60 patents have been filed under design, innovations in service autonomy, ease of use and connectivity.  ZOE is fitted with a ""Range Optimizer"" system which enhances the battery life, whatever the driving conditions. As a vehicles thermal speed, altitude, your driving style, the use of heating or air conditioning, all have an influence on the battery range. On a suburban route, you can generally achieve around 100km during the winter season and 150km in the summer. To recharge ZOE’s battery, simply plug it in - the charger chameleon adapts to the available power (between minimum power of 3kW and 43kW of maximum power). Call a friend? Meet in town? Check your emails because you are late? You can do anything with the Renault R-Link, touch screen integrated multimedia. And besides that, it's easy!"

title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır.  Her 3 günde 1 yeni video yayınladığımızı hatırlatır, yeni videolarımızdan haberdar olmanız için, kanalımıza abone olduktan sonra bildirimleri açmanızı önemle rica ederiz. title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track. title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge. title: Discover the New Renault ZOE
description: "Title: All Is Calm Artist: Whinnie Williams  Song: That's Entertainment Director: Carl Rinsch  ZOE integrates the most advanced electric technology. More than 60 patents have been filed under design, innovations in service autonomy, ease of use and connectivity.  ZOE is fitted with a ""Range Optimizer"" system which enhances the battery life, whatever the driving conditions. As a vehicles thermal speed, altitude, your driving style, the use of heating or air conditioning, all have an influence on the battery range. On a suburban route, you can generally achieve around 100km during the winter season and 150km in the summer. To recharge ZOE’s battery, simply plug it in - the charger chameleon adapts to the available power (between minimum power of 3kW and 43kW of maximum power). Call a friend? Meet in town? Check your emails because you are late? You can do anything with the Renault R-Link, touch screen integrated multimedia. And besides that, it's easy!"

title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır.  Her 3 günde 1 yeni video yayınladığımızı hatırlatır, yeni videolarımızdan haberdar olmanız için, kanalımıza abone olduktan sonra bildirimleri açmanızı önemle rica ederiz.  Ayrıca aşağıdaki sosyal medya hesaplarımızı takip ederseniz seviniriz. title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge. title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track. title: Discover the New Renault ZOE
description: "Title: All Is Calm Artist: Whinnie Williams  Song: That's Entertainment Director: Carl Rinsch  ZOE integrates the most advanced electric technology. More than 60 patents have been filed under design, innovations in service autonomy, ease of use and connectivity.  ZOE is fitted with a ""Range Optimizer"" system which enhances the battery life, whatever the driving conditions. As a vehicles thermal speed, altitude, your driving style, the use of heating or air conditioning, all have an influence on the battery range. On a suburban route, you can generally achieve around 100km during the winter season and 150km in the summer. To recharge ZOE’s battery, simply plug it in - the charger chameleon adapts to the available power (between minimum power of 3kW and 43kW of maximum power). Call a friend? Meet in town? Check your emails because you are late? You can do anything with the Renault R-Link, touch screen integrated multimedia. And besides that, it's easy!"

title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır.  Her 3 günde 1 yeni video yayınladığımızı hatırlatır, yeni videolarımızdan haberdar olmanız için, kanalımıza abone olduktan sonra bildirimleri açmanızı önemle rica ederiz.  Ayrıca aşağıdaki sosyal medya hesaplarımızı takip ederseniz seviniriz. title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge. title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track. title: Discover the New Renault ZOE
description: "Title: All Is Calm Artist: Whinnie Williams  Song: That's Entertainment Director: Carl Rinsch  ZOE integrates the most advanced electric technology. More than 60 patents have been filed under design, innovations in service autonomy, ease of use and connectivity.  ZOE is fitted with a ""Range Optimizer"" system which enhances the battery life, whatever the driving conditions. As a vehicles thermal speed, altitude, your driving style, the use of heating or air conditioning, all have an influence on the battery range. On a suburban route, you can generally achieve around 100km during the winter season and 150km in the summer. To recharge ZOE’s battery, simply plug it in - the charger chameleon adapts to the available power (between minimum power of 3kW and 43kW of maximum power). Call a friend? Meet in town? Check your emails because you are late? You can do anything with the Renault R-Link, touch screen integrated multimedia. And besides that, it's easy!"

title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır.  Her 3 günde 1 yeni video yayınladığımızı hatırlatır, yeni videolarımızdan haberdar olmanız için, kanalımıza abone olduktan sonra bildirimleri açmanızı önemle rica ederiz. title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge. title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track. title: Discover the New Renault ZOE
description: "Title: All Is Calm Artist: Whinnie Williams  Song: That's Entertainment Director: Carl Rinsch  ZOE integrates the most advanced electric technology. More than 60 patents have been filed under design, innovations in service autonomy, ease of use and connectivity.  ZOE is fitted with a ""Range Optimizer"" system which enhances the battery life, whatever the driving conditions. As a vehicles thermal speed, altitude, your driving style, the use of heating or air conditioning, all have an influence on the battery range. On a suburban route, you can generally achieve around 100km during the winter season and 150km in the summer. To recharge ZOE’s battery, simply plug it in - the charger chameleon adapts to the available power (between minimum power of 3kW and 43kW of maximum power). Call a friend? Meet in town? Check your emails because you are late? You can do anything with the Renault R-Link, touch screen integrated multimedia. And besides that, it's easy!"

title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır.  Her 3 günde 1 yeni video yayınladığımızı hatırlatır, yeni videolarımızdan haberdar olmanız için, kanalımıza abone olduktan sonra bildirimleri açmanızı önemle rica ederiz.  Ayrıca aşağıdaki sosyal medya hesaplarımızı takip ederseniz seviniriz. title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge. title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track.   If you love cars you should subscribe now to official YouCar's channel: http://urlz.fr/lEd Go! It's free!  All the Best. title: Discover the New Renault ZOE
description: "Title: All Is Calm Artist: Whinnie Williams  Song: That's Entertainment Director: Carl Rinsch  ZOE integrates the most advanced electric technology. More than 60 patents have been filed under design, innovations in service autonomy, ease of use and connectivity.  ZOE is fitted with a ""Range Optimizer"" system which enhances the battery life, whatever the driving conditions. As a vehicles thermal speed, altitude, your driving style, the use of heating or air conditioning, all have an influence on the battery range. On a suburban route, you can generally achieve around 100km during the winter season and 150km in the summer. To recharge ZOE’s battery, simply plug it in - the charger chameleon adapts to the available power (between minimum power of 3kW and 43kW of maximum power). Call a friend? Meet in town? Check your emails because you are late? You can do anything with the Renault R-Link, touch screen integrated multimedia. And besides that, it's easy!"

title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır.  Her 3 günde 1 yeni video yayınladığımızı hatırlatır, yeni videolarımızdan haberdar olmanız için, kanalımıza abone olduktan sonra bildirimleri açmanızı önemle rica ederiz. title: AdBuster - Renault Megane Destroy!
description: FAQ:   1. Dlaczego nie oddałeś go potrzebującej rodzinie, bydlaku?!  - bo samochód nie nadawał się do dalszego użytkowania. Wszystko było przerdzewiałe na wylot, a usterki nie do naprawienia. Lewarek wbijał się w podłogę.  2. Jakich uszkodzeń doznał samochód podczas distroju?  - niewielkich. Poszły 3 szyby, lusterko i wewnętrzna lampka. Prawy tylny klosz pękł przy uderzeniu w ścianę (stłuczka parkingowa). Poza tym parę wgniotów i urwana osłona silnika.  3. Czemu tak słabo go zdemolowałeś? Ja bym zrobił to tak: bla bla...  - bo jeszcze trzeba było dojechać nim przez miasto na skup złomu. Mógłbym na lawecie, ale KOSZTA  4. Co to za muzyczka w tle?   - autorstwa Kevina McLeod'a, pod licencją Creative Commons  5. Co to za chujowy filmik, miałeś robić konfrontacje! @#$%^  - bo od czasu do czasu lubię coś rozwalić i wrzucić to na YT.  6. Dodaj mnie do znajomych, plox.  - najpierw musimy wypić razem browara. title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge. title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track. title: Discover the New Renault ZOE
description: "Title: All Is Calm Artist: Whinnie Williams  Song: That's Entertainment Director: Carl Rinsch  ZOE integrates the most advanced electric technology. More than 60 patents have been filed under design, innovations in service autonomy, ease of use and connectivity.  ZOE is fitted with a ""Range Optimizer"" system which enhances the battery life, whatever the driving conditions. As a vehicles thermal speed, altitude, your driving style, the use of heating or air conditioning, all have an influence on the battery range. On a suburban route, you can generally achieve around 100km during the winter season and 150km in the summer. To recharge ZOE’s battery, simply plug it in - the charger chameleon adapts to the available power (between minimum power of 3kW and 43kW of maximum power). Call a friend? Meet in town? Check your emails because you are late? You can do anything with the Renault R-Link, touch screen integrated multimedia. And besides that, it's easy!"

title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır.  Her 3 günde 1 yeni video yayınladığımızı hatırlatır, yeni videolarımızdan haberdar olmanız için, kanalımıza abone olduktan sonra bildirimleri açmanızı önemle rica ederiz.  Ayrıca aşağıdaki sosyal medya hesaplarımızı takip ederseniz seviniriz. title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge.  Tot Gear Video - next week  Thanks to Chips Films for making a great video  http://chipsfilms.com/about/  Watch Charlie bit my finger: http://bit.ly/HDCYT_Charliebitme  T-Shirts http://charliebitme.firebrandstore.com/ iPhone  http://itunes.apple.com/gb/app/charlie-bit-me!!!/id494858348?mt=8 Android  https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.viralspiral.charlie  Twitter http://twitter.com/harryandcharlie

title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track. title: Discover the New Renault ZOE
description: "Title: All Is Calm Artist: Whinnie Williams  Song: That's Entertainment Director: Carl Rinsch  ZOE integrates the most advanced electric technology. More than 60 patents have been filed under design, innovations in service autonomy, ease of use and connectivity.  ZOE is fitted with a ""Range Optimizer"" system which enhances the battery life, whatever the driving conditions. As a vehicles thermal speed, altitude, your driving style, the use of heating or air conditioning, all have an influence on the battery range. On a suburban route, you can generally achieve around 100km during the winter season and 150km in the summer. To recharge ZOE’s battery, simply plug it in - the charger chameleon adapts to the available power (between minimum power of 3kW and 43kW of maximum power). Call a friend? Meet in town? Check your emails because you are late? You can do anything with the Renault R-Link, touch screen integrated multimedia. And besides that, it's easy!"

title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır.  Her 3 günde 1 yeni video yayınladığımızı hatırlatır, yeni videolarımızdan haberdar olmanız için, kanalımıza abone olduktan sonra bildirimleri açmanızı önemle rica ederiz.  Ayrıca aşağıdaki sosyal medya hesaplarımızı takip ederseniz seviniriz. Co to za chujowy filmik, miałeś robić konfrontacje! @#$%^  - bo od czasu do czasu lubię coś rozwalić i wrzucić to na YT.  6. Dodaj mnie do znajomych, plox.  - najpierw musimy wypić razem browara. title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge. title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track. title: Discover the New Renault ZOE
description: "Title: All Is Calm Artist: Whinnie Williams  Song: That's Entertainment Director: Carl Rinsch  ZOE integrates the most advanced electric technology. More than 60 patents have been filed under design, innovations in service autonomy, ease of use and connectivity.  ZOE is fitted with a ""Range Optimizer"" system which enhances the battery life, whatever the driving conditions. As a vehicles thermal speed, altitude, your driving style, the use of heating or air conditioning, all have an influence on the battery range. On a suburban route, you can generally achieve around 100km during the winter season and 150km in the summer. To recharge ZOE’s battery, simply plug it in - the charger chameleon adapts to the available power (between minimum power of 3kW and 43kW of maximum power). Call a friend? Meet in town? Check your emails because you are late? You can do anything with the Renault R-Link, touch screen integrated multimedia. And besides that, it's easy!"

title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır.  Her 3 günde 1 yeni video yayınladığımızı hatırlatır, yeni videolarımızdan haberdar olmanız için, kanalımıza abone olduktan sonra bildirimleri açmanızı önemle rica ederiz.  Ayrıca aşağıdaki sosyal medya hesaplarımızı takip ederseniz seviniriz. title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge. title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track. title: Discover the New Renault ZOE
description: "Title: All Is Calm Artist: Whinnie Williams  Song: That's Entertainment Director: Carl Rinsch  ZOE integrates the most advanced electric technology. More than 60 patents have been filed under design, innovations in service autonomy, ease of use and connectivity.  ZOE is fitted with a ""Range Optimizer"" system which enhances the battery life, whatever the driving conditions. As a vehicles thermal speed, altitude, your driving style, the use of heating or air conditioning, all have an influence on the battery range. On a suburban route, you can generally achieve around 100km during the winter season and 150km in the summer. To recharge ZOE’s battery, simply plug it in - the charger chameleon adapts to the available power (between minimum power of 3kW and 43kW of maximum power). Call a friend? Meet in town? Check your emails because you are late? You can do anything with the Renault R-Link, touch screen integrated multimedia. And besides that, it's easy!"

title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır.  Her 3 günde 1 yeni video yayınladığımızı hatırlatır, yeni videolarımızdan haberdar olmanız için, kanalımıza abone olduktan sonra bildirimleri açmanızı önemle rica ederiz. title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge. title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track. title: Discover the New Renault ZOE
description: "Title: All Is Calm Artist: Whinnie Williams  Song: That's Entertainment Director: Carl Rinsch  ZOE integrates the most advanced electric technology. More than 60 patents have been filed under design, innovations in service autonomy, ease of use and connectivity.  ZOE is fitted with a ""Range Optimizer"" system which enhances the battery life, whatever the driving conditions. As a vehicles thermal speed, altitude, your driving style, the use of heating or air conditioning, all have an influence on the battery range. On a suburban route, you can generally achieve around 100km during the winter season and 150km in the summer. To recharge ZOE’s battery, simply plug it in - the charger chameleon adapts to the available power (between minimum power of 3kW and 43kW of maximum power). Call a friend? Meet in town? Check your emails because you are late? You can do anything with the Renault R-Link, touch screen integrated multimedia. And besides that, it's easy!"

title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır.  Her 3 günde 1 yeni video yayınladığımızı hatırlatır, yeni videolarımızdan haberdar olmanız için, kanalımıza abone olduktan sonra bildirimleri açmanızı önemle rica ederiz.  Ayrıca aşağıdaki sosyal medya hesaplarımızı takip ederseniz seviniriz. title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge. title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track. title: Discover the New Renault ZOE
description: "Title: All Is Calm Artist: Whinnie Williams  Song: That's Entertainment Director: Carl Rinsch  ZOE integrates the most advanced electric technology. More than 60 patents have been filed under design, innovations in service autonomy, ease of use and connectivity.  ZOE is fitted with a ""Range Optimizer"" system which enhances the battery life, whatever the driving conditions. As a vehicles thermal speed, altitude, your driving style, the use of heating or air conditioning, all have an influence on the battery range. On a suburban route, you can generally achieve around 100km during the winter season and 150km in the summer. To recharge ZOE’s battery, simply plug it in - the charger chameleon adapts to the available power (between minimum power of 3kW and 43kW of maximum power). Call a friend? Meet in town? Check your emails because you are late? You can do anything with the Renault R-Link, touch screen integrated multimedia. And besides that, it's easy!"

title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır.  Her 3 günde 1 yeni video yayınladığımızı hatırlatır, yeni videolarımızdan haberdar olmanız için, kanalımıza abone olduktan sonra bildirimleri açmanızı önemle rica ederiz.  Ayrıca aşağıdaki sosyal medya hesaplarımızı takip ederseniz seviniriz. title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge. title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track. title: Fiat Uno Turbo vs Renault 5 Gt Turbo: LE BARE! - Davide Cironi Drive Experience (SUBS)
description: Le bare anni '80 vanno elaborate, altrimenti noi maschi non siamo contenti. Non è un confronto, non ci sono schede tecniche, è un test tutto sbagliato, ma ci sono 500 cv da frustare! http://www.driveexperience.it/shop/  SCHEDE TECNICHE:  Fiat Uno Turbo: -Motore 1.4cc -Bielle acciaio H rovesciato -Pistoni stampati -Testata lavorata nei condotti -Valvole in nimonic maggiorate sia di aspirazione che di scarico -Albero a camme lavorato -Collettori scarico in acciaio -Marmitta title: Discover the New Renault ZOE
description: "Title: All Is Calm Artist: Whinnie Williams  Song: That's Entertainment Director: Carl Rinsch  ZOE integrates the most advanced electric technology. More than 60 patents have been filed under design, innovations in service autonomy, ease of use and connectivity.  ZOE is fitted with a ""Range Optimizer"" system which enhances the battery life, whatever the driving conditions. As a vehicles thermal speed, altitude, your driving style, the use of heating or air conditioning, all have an influence on the battery range. On a suburban route, you can generally achieve around 100km during the winter season and 150km in the summer. To recharge ZOE’s battery, simply plug it in - the charger chameleon adapts to the available power (between minimum power of 3kW and 43kW of maximum power). Call a friend? Meet in town? Check your emails because you are late? You can do anything with the Renault R-Link, touch screen integrated multimedia. And besides that, it's easy!"

title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır.  Her 3 günde 1 yeni video yayınladığımızı hatırlatır, yeni videolarımızdan haberdar olmanız için, kanalımıza abone olduktan sonra bildirimleri açmanızı önemle rica ederiz.  Ayrıca aşağıdaki sosyal medya hesaplarımızı takip ederseniz seviniriz.
