title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge. title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track. title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır.  Her 3 günde 1 yeni video yayınladığımızı hatırlatır, yeni videolarımızdan haberdar olmanız için, kanalımıza abone olduktan sonra bildirimleri açmanızı önemle rica ederiz.  Ayrıca aşağıdaki sosyal medya hesaplarımızı takip ederseniz seviniriz. title: Crash Test Renault
description: Um video propaganda da renault, que ganhou 5 estrelas no Euro NCAP Crashtest, um crashtest famoso. Muito maneiro ver aqueles carros feiosos sendo desfigurados, eu realmente acho que a renault não acerta nos carros que ela faz. Tem carro batendo de frente, arrastando um na lateral do outro, todos sendo destruídos. Tem até uma hora que dois carros em rota de colisão saltam sobre outros dois e colidem no ar. As câmeras de alta resolução e velocidade com a música clássica ao fundo dão a sensação de suavidade e tranquilidade, um verdadeiro balé automobilístico. Gostei.

description: FAQ:   1. Dlaczego nie oddałeś go potrzebującej rodzinie, bydlaku?!  - bo samochód nie nadawał się do dalszego użytkowania. Poszły 3 szyby, lusterko i wewnętrzna lampka. Prawy tylny klosz pękł przy uderzeniu w ścianę (stłuczka parkingowa). Poza tym parę wgniotów i urwana osłona silnika.  3. Co to za chujowy filmik, miałeś robić konfrontacje! @#$%^  - bo od czasu do czasu lubię coś rozwalić i wrzucić to na YT.  6. Dodaj mnie do znajomych, plox.  - najpierw musimy wypić razem browara. title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge. title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track. title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır.  Her 3 günde 1 yeni video yayınladığımızı hatırlatır, yeni videolarımızdan haberdar olmanız için, kanalımıza abone olduktan sonra bildirimleri açmanızı önemle rica ederiz.  Ayrıca aşağıdaki sosyal medya hesaplarımızı takip ederseniz seviniriz. title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge. title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track. title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır. title: Crash Test Renault
description: Um video propaganda da renault, que ganhou 5 estrelas no Euro NCAP Crashtest, um crashtest famoso. Tem carro batendo de frente, arrastando um na lateral do outro, todos sendo destruídos. Tem até uma hora que dois carros em rota de colisão saltam sobre outros dois e colidem no ar. As câmeras de alta resolução e velocidade com a música clássica ao fundo dão a sensação de suavidade e tranquilidade, um verdadeiro balé automobilístico. Gostei.

title: AdBuster - Renault Megane Destroy!
description: FAQ:   1. Dlaczego nie oddałeś go potrzebującej rodzinie, bydlaku?!  - bo samochód nie nadawał się do dalszego użytkowania. Wszystko było przerdzewiałe na wylot, a usterki nie do naprawienia. Lewarek wbijał się w podłogę.  2. Jakich uszkodzeń doznał samochód podczas distroju?  - niewielkich. Poszły 3 szyby, lusterko i wewnętrzna lampka. Prawy tylny klosz pękł przy uderzeniu w ścianę (stłuczka parkingowa). Poza tym parę wgniotów i urwana osłona silnika.  3. Czemu tak słabo go zdemolowałeś? Ja bym zrobił to tak: bla bla...  - bo jeszcze trzeba było dojechać nim przez miasto na skup złomu. Mógłbym na lawecie, ale KOSZTA  4. Co to za muzyczka w tle?   - autorstwa Kevina McLeod'a, pod licencją Creative Commons  5. Co to za chujowy filmik, miałeś robić konfrontacje! @#$%^  - bo od czasu do czasu lubię coś rozwalić i wrzucić to na YT.  6. Dodaj mnie do znajomych, plox.  - najpierw musimy wypić razem browara. title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge. title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track. title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır.  Her 3 günde 1 yeni video yayınladığımızı hatırlatır, yeni videolarımızdan haberdar olmanız için, kanalımıza abone olduktan sonra bildirimleri açmanızı önemle rica ederiz.  Ayrıca aşağıdaki sosyal medya hesaplarımızı takip ederseniz seviniriz. Tem carro batendo de frente, arrastando um na lateral do outro, todos sendo destruídos. Tem até uma hora que dois carros em rota de colisão saltam sobre outros dois e colidem no ar. As câmeras de alta resolução e velocidade com a música clássica ao fundo dão a sensação de suavidade e tranquilidade, um verdadeiro balé automobilístico. Gostei.

title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge. title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track. title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır.  Her 3 günde 1 yeni video yayınladığımızı hatırlatır, yeni videolarımızdan haberdar olmanız için, kanalımıza abone olduktan sonra bildirimleri açmanızı önemle rica ederiz.  Ayrıca aşağıdaki sosyal medya hesaplarımızı takip ederseniz seviniriz. title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge. title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track. Description: I filmed this awesome Renault 5 Maxi Turbo by AP Motorsport in action. In the video you can see some details of the car, interior and exterior, listen to the start up of the engine, and watch some launches, acceleration and fly bys. I fitted my GoPro on board and next to the exhaust to take the pure sound, some flames and backfire. Many thanks to the Team of AP Motorsport. Stay tuned for Step 2.  Ho filmato questa splendida Renault 5 Maxi Turbo by AP Motorsport in azione. Nel video potete vedere alcuni dettagli dell'auto, interni ed esterni, ascoltare il sound del motore durante l'accensione e vedere delle partenze, accelerazioni e passaggi in velocità. Ho montato la Gopro a bordo dell'auto e di fianco allo scarico per registrare il sound e le fiammate nei ritorni. Mille grazie al Team AP Motorsport. State collegati per lo step 2!

title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır.  Her 3 günde 1 yeni video yayınladığımızı hatırlatır, yeni videolarımızdan haberdar olmanız için, kanalımıza abone olduktan sonra bildirimleri açmanızı önemle rica ederiz.  Ayrıca aşağıdaki sosyal medya hesaplarımızı takip ederseniz seviniriz. title: Crash Test Renault
description: Um video propaganda da renault, que ganhou 5 estrelas no Euro NCAP Crashtest, um crashtest famoso. Muito maneiro ver aqueles carros feiosos sendo desfigurados, eu realmente acho que a renault não acerta nos carros que ela faz. Tem carro batendo de frente, arrastando um na lateral do outro, todos sendo destruídos. Tem até uma hora que dois carros em rota de colisão saltam sobre outros dois e colidem no ar. As câmeras de alta resolução e velocidade com a música clássica ao fundo dão a sensação de suavidade e tranquilidade, um verdadeiro balé automobilístico. Gostei.

title: AdBuster - Renault Megane Destroy!
description: FAQ:   1. Dlaczego nie oddałeś go potrzebującej rodzinie, bydlaku?!  - bo samochód nie nadawał się do dalszego użytkowania. Wszystko było przerdzewiałe na wylot, a usterki nie do naprawienia. Lewarek wbijał się w podłogę.  2. Jakich uszkodzeń doznał samochód podczas distroju?  - niewielkich. Poszły 3 szyby, lusterko i wewnętrzna lampka. Prawy tylny klosz pękł przy uderzeniu w ścianę (stłuczka parkingowa). Poza tym parę wgniotów i urwana osłona silnika.  3. Czemu tak słabo go zdemolowałeś? Ja bym zrobił to tak: bla bla...  - bo jeszcze trzeba było dojechać nim przez miasto na skup złomu. Mógłbym na lawecie, ale KOSZTA  4. Co to za muzyczka w tle?   - autorstwa Kevina McLeod'a, pod licencją Creative Commons  5. Co to za chujowy filmik, miałeś robić konfrontacje! @#$%^  - bo od czasu do czasu lubię coś rozwalić i wrzucić to na YT.  6. Dodaj mnie do znajomych, plox.  - najpierw musimy wypić razem browara.   Tymczasem możesz zalajkowacz mnie na moim fanpejdżu: http://www.facebook.com/adbuster  Pozdro!

title: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV
description: Charlie Bit the family Renault ZOE EV. Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1oHVuUM  We were very lucky to be asked by Renault for the family to try out their new battery-powered car and make a fun video about it.  The other lucky thing is that we did not need to do the filming ourselves.  We are usually a really big family of six but Rupert, who is our youngest, was with his grandparents for the day, leaving us still a big-sized family of five.    The idea was to see if the Renault ZOE was a great family car.  So what else should we do than pack in a really busy day visiting a number of places all over the county.  We also thought the only way of doing videos the way we do videos was to spoof perhaps the most famous of car programmes 'Top Gear' (more on that next week).  We all had great fun, enjoyed the car and we loved the way the videos turned out and are therefore proud to share these with you.   Information about the video Places Visited; The Snow Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thesnowcentre.com/ XC Centre Hemel Hempstead    http://www.thexc.co.uk/ Hell Fire Caves High Wycombe    http://www.hellfirecaves.co.uk/ Round trip approximately 90 miles.  Renault ZOE Information The Renault ZOE has a range of about 100 miles. We used apps on smart phones and the Renault ZOE satellite navigation system to choose suitable charging stations There are a number of ways to charge the car. Fast charged (about 30 minutes) for a full charge from dedicated stations, slower options and from a domestic source at home.  Around London = No congestion charge. title: Renault Mégane 4 (2016) PRODUCTION
description: Kadjar and New Mégane are based on the Renault-Nissan Alliance’s new modular architecture, CMF C/D  (for “Common Module Family”), much like New Espace and Talisman (built at the Douai plant in France).   With a modular architecture, different vehicles share inter-compatible subsystems not visible to the customer, with the attendant cost rationalization advantages. Specifically, this concerns the engine compartment, cockpit, front under-body unit, rear under-body unit and electrical and electronic subsystems.   Aspects visible to the customer, on the other hand, are highly diverse. At the Palencia assembly line, with its large “S” shape specially adapted to the dimensions of the new cars, operators have to manage very extensive diversity in vehicle equipment and the workstations to handle them. Examples include the 4Control system, available on New Mégane GT, four-wheel drive, available on Kadjar, and a broad choice of wheels, with a parts counts that approaches a hundred different items.  One hundred percent of vehicles undergo appearance and functionality tests as they come off the production line, prior to dynamic testing on an outdoor test track. title: Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test
description: ...  Renault Twizy 2017 Baba Oğul Test videosu ile karşınızdayız. Renault Nissan Mitsubishi Grubu’nda faaliyet gösteren Fransız Renault markasının yüzde 100 elektrikli aracı Twizy, 17 HP güç ve 57 Nm tork üreten elektrikli motor ve lityum iyon pillere sahip. Motosiklet ruhsatlı Twizy, 2338 mm uzunluğa, 1381 mm genişliğe, 1454 mm yüksekliğe ve 1686 mm dingil mesafesine sahip. İki kişinin, tıpkı motosikletlerdeki gibi arka arkaya oturduğu Twizy’de dört adet 13 inç’lik tekerlek ve direksiyon simidi bulunuyor. Radyo ve klimanın yer almadığı araçta 31 litrelik bir bagajın yanı sıra biri 3.5, diğeri ise 5 litrelik iki adet kapaklı torpidoya yer verilmiş. Renault Twizy’nin koltuk altlarında yer alan bataryası, 3 metrelik bir kablo yardımıyla ev tipi prizden 3 buçuk saatte dolduruluyor. Aracın tam dolu pillerle menzili ise 70-80 km. 1 ileri otomatik şanzımanla kumanda edilen Twizy’de sadece sürücü hava yastığı bulunuyor. Kapıları yukarıya doğru açılan aracın maksimum hızı 80 km/s, 0-45 km/s hızlanma süresi ise 6.1 saniye. Twizy’nin boş ağırlığı 474 kg, akü kapasitesi ise 6.1 kW/s. Kullanımda sıfır salıma sahip Renault Twizy’nin elektrikli motoru, arka koltuğun altına yerleştirilmiş. Renault ZOE gibi tamamen elektrikli bir araç olan Twizy’nin 2017 fiyatı 46.900 TL. Piller bu fiyata dahil.   Dünyada ilk kez, otomobil editörü bir baba (Emre Anamur), çekimlere oğlu 3 yaş 3 aylıkken başlayarak (Selim Anamur, Ocak 2018'de 5 yaşında olacak) otomobil test videoları çekip yayınlıyor. Bu eğlenceli ama aynı zaman da bilgi dolu videoları ilgiyle izlemenizi diler, izledikten sonra beğenmenizi, yorumlamanızı ve kanalımıza abone olmanızı rica ederiz. Böylece kanalımız büyüyecek, daha fazla kişiye ulaşacaktır.  Her 3 günde 1 yeni video yayınladığımızı hatırlatır, yeni videolarımızdan haberdar olmanız için, kanalımıza abone olduktan sonra bildirimleri açmanızı önemle rica ederiz.  Ayrıca aşağıdaki sosyal medya hesaplarımızı takip ederseniz seviniriz. title: 8 New Renault Cars to Buy in the Upcoming Year (Updated Models of 2019)
description: Renault is one of those companies that does not get hyped up by the media, but still manages to sell loads of cars, shows steady growth and slowly takes over the world. In fact, their acquisition of Nissan and Mitsubishi brands actually made this alliance the biggest in the world by the production volume. In today’s episode we will demonstrate the new arrivals in the Renault’s lineup, that span across all body styles, include new electric cars and pose tough competition to other brands.  2019 MODELS FROM OTHER MANUFACTURERS PLAYLIST #ATcars2019: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vJZPVWPQcnQ&list=PLouyd8mRhOO7KDhZMYTpvi3n8Pb6nnjqN  You are watching #AutomotiveTerritoryDailyNews ! Subscribe to stay informed about the newcomers of the auto world and lets start the engines!  0:40 #1 2019 Renault Kadjar   2019 Renault Kadjar is one of three models in Renault’s crossover lineup that shares its exterior styling with smaller Captur and larger Koleos. It enters the 2019 model year with a refreshed face, new gasoline engine, and updated trim levels.  1:51 #2 2019 Renault Megane R.S. Trophy  To compete with the current leaders the likes of VW Golf R, Honda Civic Type R and Mercedes AMG A35, Renault upgraded their top notch Megane R.S. with the Trophy modification for the 2019.  3:01 #3 2019 Renault Talisman  In 2019, Renault Talisman receives a racier limited version called S-Edition. It features more standard tech and a powerful 1.8L gasoline engine delivering 225 hp and 221 lb-ft of torque.  4:11 #4 2020 Renault Arcana  The coupe SUV design was rather popular in 2018 across multiple manufacturers, so Renault also decided to get a piece of the sales pie. The new crossover Arcana was developed by the joined effort of the Renault’s French and Russian teams.  5:17 #5 2019 Renault K-ZE  The new electric car from Renault will be named K-ZE hinting its being based on the subcompact crossover Kwid which is currently sold in India at a ridiculously low price of $5,000.  6:25 #6 2019 Alpine A110 and A110 GT4   2019 Alpine A110 was unveiled in three iterations, a track-only racer called GT4 and two road-legal models, Pure and Légende. All share a 1.8L turbocharged 4-cylinder netting 270 and 252 horses respectively.  7:43 #7 2019 Renault EZ Ultimo  The most recent representation of Renault’s vision of the future was depicted in the trio of concepts based on the home platform, all of which are fully autonomous and electric. The most impressive one is undoubtedly the EZ-Ultimo.  8:54 #8 2019 Renault Zoe  Renault Zoe is the bestselling European electric car on the market, that fits the demand for compact urban commuters, that can squeeze through narrow streets and at the same time gives access to the no pollution zones.

title: Renault Talisman (ENG) - Test Drive and Review
description: Help me make better reviews by donating: http://patreon.com/marekdrives https://www.paypal.me/MarekDrives  My gear: Camera: http://amzn.to/2anPsaz Lens1 http://amzn.to/2adPOO0 Lens2 http://amzn.to/2adPSNN Mic1 http://amzn.to/2amPI6c Mic2 http://amzn.to/2aATyM1 Windscreen http://amzn.to/2aESbNt GoPro1 http://amzn.to/2arzGsL GoPro2 http://amzn.to/2adQ9Qz Gimbal http://amzn.to/2aCVwZX GoPro suction cup http://amzn.to/2anS0oQ Drone http://amzn.to/2anS8VB Tripod1 http://amzn.to/2anRY08 Tripod2 http://amzn.to/2a9E1V9 Travel Tripod http://amzn.to/2adQcw1 Slider http://amzn.to/2adQS4f Suction mount1 http://amzn.to/2anRJT1 + http://amzn.to/2adQSkZ Suction mount2 http://amzn.to/2a9E9UZ Camera bag http://amzn.to/2boAxNo Camera case http://amzn.to/2bpvIS0 Laptop http://amzn.to/2amBuIP  Renault Talisman replaces not just the Laguna, but also the less popular, more upscale Latitude. Sales in the D segment are gradually declining, as people prefer family minivans, crossovers, and increasingly big compact cars. Hence Renault decided to target the more refined buyer looking for a true executive car, rather than just a big family car. Thanks to 4Control Talisman is very maneuverable at low speeds, and stable at high speeds. This is a 4-wheel steering system, which you get among others on some Porsches. At low speeds Renault's rear wheels turn in the opposite direction to the front wheels, giving you tighter turning. And at high speeds all wheels turn in the same direction, so Talisman goes better through fast corners. title: RENAULT - Evolution From 1898-2018
description: RENAULT - Evolution From 1898-2018 Groupe Renault is a French multinational automobile manufacturer established in 1899. The company produces a range of cars and vans, and in the past has manufactured trucks, tractors, tanks, buses/coaches and autorail vehicles. According to the Organisation Internationale des Constructeurs d'Automobiles, in 2016 Renault was the ninth biggest automaker in the world by production volume. The Renault–Nissan–Mitsubishi Alliance is the fourth-largest automotive group. Headquartered in Boulogne-Billancourt, near Paris, the Renault group is made up of the namesake Renault marque and subsidiaries, Alpine, Automobile Dacia from Romania, Renault Samsung Motors from South Korea, and AvtoVAZ from Russia. Renault has a 43.4% controlling stake in Nissan of Japan, and a 1.55% stake in Daimler AG of Germany (since 2012, Renault manufactures engines for the Daimler's Mercedes A-Class and B-Class cars). Renault also owns subsidiaries RCI Banque (automotive financing), Renault Retail Group (automotive distribution) and Motrio (automotive parts). Renault has various joint ventures, including Oyak-Renault (Turkey), Renault Pars (Iran). Carlos Ghosn is the current chairman and CEO. The French government owns a 15% share of Renault. title: 8 New Renault Cars to Buy in the Upcoming Year (Updated Models of 2019)
description: Renault is one of those companies that does not get hyped up by the media, but still manages to sell loads of cars, shows steady growth and slowly takes over the world. In fact, their acquisition of Nissan and Mitsubishi brands actually made this alliance the biggest in the world by the production volume. In today’s episode we will demonstrate the new arrivals in the Renault’s lineup, that span across all body styles, include new electric cars and pose tough competition to other brands.  2019 MODELS FROM OTHER MANUFACTURERS PLAYLIST #ATcars2019: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vJZPVWPQcnQ&list=PLouyd8mRhOO7KDhZMYTpvi3n8Pb6nnjqN  You are watching #AutomotiveTerritoryDailyNews ! Subscribe to stay informed about the newcomers of the auto world and lets start the engines!  0:40 #1 2019 Renault Kadjar   2019 Renault Kadjar is one of three models in Renault’s crossover lineup that shares its exterior styling with smaller Captur and larger Koleos. It enters the 2019 model year with a refreshed face, new gasoline engine, and updated trim levels.  1:51 #2 2019 Renault Megane R.S. Trophy  To compete with the current leaders the likes of VW Golf R, Honda Civic Type R and Mercedes AMG A35, Renault upgraded their top notch Megane R.S. with the Trophy modification for the 2019.  3:01 #3 2019 Renault Talisman  In 2019, Renault Talisman receives a racier limited version called S-Edition. It features more standard tech and a powerful 1.8L gasoline engine delivering 225 hp and 221 lb-ft of torque.  4:11 #4 2020 Renault Arcana  The coupe SUV design was rather popular in 2018 across multiple manufacturers, so Renault also decided to get a piece of the sales pie. The new crossover Arcana was developed by the joined effort of the Renault’s French and Russian teams.  5:17 #5 2019 Renault K-ZE  The new electric car from Renault will be named K-ZE hinting its being based on the subcompact crossover Kwid which is currently sold in India at a ridiculously low price of $5,000.  6:25 #6 2019 Alpine A110 and A110 GT4   2019 Alpine A110 was unveiled in three iterations, a track-only racer called GT4 and two road-legal models, Pure and Légende. All share a 1.8L turbocharged 4-cylinder netting 270 and 252 horses respectively.  7:43 #7 2019 Renault EZ Ultimo  The most recent representation of Renault’s vision of the future was depicted in the trio of concepts based on the home platform, all of which are fully autonomous and electric. The most impressive one is undoubtedly the EZ-Ultimo.  8:54 #8 2019 Renault Zoe  Renault Zoe is the bestselling European electric car on the market, that fits the demand for compact urban commuters, that can squeeze through narrow streets and at the same time gives access to the no pollution zones.

title: RENAULT - Evolution From 1898-2018
description: RENAULT - Evolution From 1898-2018 Groupe Renault is a French multinational automobile manufacturer established in 1899. The company produces a range of cars and vans, and in the past has manufactured trucks, tractors, tanks, buses/coaches and autorail vehicles. According to the Organisation Internationale des Constructeurs d'Automobiles, in 2016 Renault was the ninth biggest automaker in the world by production volume. The Renault–Nissan–Mitsubishi Alliance is the fourth-largest automotive group. Headquartered in Boulogne-Billancourt, near Paris, the Renault group is made up of the namesake Renault marque and subsidiaries, Alpine, Automobile Dacia from Romania, Renault Samsung Motors from South Korea, and AvtoVAZ from Russia. Renault has a 43.4% controlling stake in Nissan of Japan, and a 1.55% stake in Daimler AG of Germany (since 2012, Renault manufactures engines for the Daimler's Mercedes A-Class and B-Class cars). Renault also owns subsidiaries RCI Banque (automotive financing), Renault Retail Group (automotive distribution) and Motrio (automotive parts). Renault has various joint ventures, including Oyak-Renault (Turkey), Renault Pars (Iran). Carlos Ghosn is the current chairman and CEO. The French government owns a 15% share of Renault. Meski mereknya Perancis, Koleos memakai pondasi Nissan X-Trail yang Jepang tulen. Sasis, suku cadang, mesin, dan transmisi adalah milik X-Trail, dan ia merupakan hasil rakitan Korea.  Jadi apa Renault Koleos ini punya karakter pribadi, atau hanya sebuah Nissan X-Trail yang ganti baju? title: Renault Clio - Prova su Strada
description: Abbiamo provato su strada la Renault Clio, una delle macchine più vendute in Italia. E abbiamo deciso di provarla in una versione un po' speciale, firmata Moschino!  Entrata in commercio nel lontano 1990, la Renault Clio ha cambiato pelle quattro volte per assecondare i gusti del mercato, e ad ogni edizione ha sempre riscontrato un ottimo successo di vendite.   L’ultima serie della Renault Clio si è posta come punto di riferimento del segmento B sia per il design fluido degli esterni, che per la qualità degli interni. In Italia, la Renault Clio è la seconda berlina più venduta dopo la Fiat Panda. title: Renault Koleos 2017 Review Indonesia | OtoDriver
description: Inilah hasil review kami akan Renault Koleos terbaru di Indonesia. Mobil ini merupakan hasil kerja sama Renault, Nissan dan Samsung.  Dengan merek Eropa, basis dari Jepang serta teknologi elektronik dari Korea, bagaimanakah rasa mobil ini?  Pada video ini reviewer OtoDriver, Fitra Eri, melompat ke balik setir Renault Koleos untuk melihat apa saja yang ditawarkan mobil ini dari berbagai sisi. Tentu saja bukan sekadar data brosur, tapi kami sampaikan pula data pengetesan kami sendiri serta impresi yang dirasakan. Mobil ini juga sudah kami tes sejauh ratusan kilometer untuk menghasilkan impresi yang akurat.  Silakan juga sambangi website kami, www.otodriver.com untuk berita terkini dan paling menarik seputar dunia otomotif. Di sana juga Anda bisa melihat review mobil-mobil terkini yang dilakukan oleh reviewer berpengalaman kami. Selain itu di www.OtoDriver.Com Anda juga dapat melakukan komparasi sendiri antar-merek mobil.   Jangan lupa klik Like bila Anda menyukai video ini, juga isi Comment tentang mobil ini atau kritik untuk perbaikan kami ke depannya. Jangan lupa juga SHARE video ini ke teman-teman Anda yang mungkin sedang membutuhkan informasi mengenai mobil.  Oh ya, jangan lupa mengisi polling kami di akhir video. title: 8 New Renault Cars to Buy in the Upcoming Year (Updated Models of 2019)
description: Renault is one of those companies that does not get hyped up by the media, but still manages to sell loads of cars, shows steady growth and slowly takes over the world. In fact, their acquisition of Nissan and Mitsubishi brands actually made this alliance the biggest in the world by the production volume. In today’s episode we will demonstrate the new arrivals in the Renault’s lineup, that span across all body styles, include new electric cars and pose tough competition to other brands.  2019 MODELS FROM OTHER MANUFACTURERS PLAYLIST #ATcars2019: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vJZPVWPQcnQ&list=PLouyd8mRhOO7KDhZMYTpvi3n8Pb6nnjqN  You are watching #AutomotiveTerritoryDailyNews ! Subscribe to stay informed about the newcomers of the auto world and lets start the engines!  0:40 #1 2019 Renault Kadjar   2019 Renault Kadjar is one of three models in Renault’s crossover lineup that shares its exterior styling with smaller Captur and larger Koleos. It enters the 2019 model year with a refreshed face, new gasoline engine, and updated trim levels.  1:51 #2 2019 Renault Megane R.S. Trophy  To compete with the current leaders the likes of VW Golf R, Honda Civic Type R and Mercedes AMG A35, Renault upgraded their top notch Megane R.S. with the Trophy modification for the 2019.  3:01 #3 2019 Renault Talisman  In 2019, Renault Talisman receives a racier limited version called S-Edition. It features more standard tech and a powerful 1.8L gasoline engine delivering 225 hp and 221 lb-ft of torque.  4:11 #4 2020 Renault Arcana  The coupe SUV design was rather popular in 2018 across multiple manufacturers, so Renault also decided to get a piece of the sales pie. The new crossover Arcana was developed by the joined effort of the Renault’s French and Russian teams.  5:17 #5 2019 Renault K-ZE  The new electric car from Renault will be named K-ZE hinting its being based on the subcompact crossover Kwid which is currently sold in India at a ridiculously low price of $5,000.  6:25 #6 2019 Alpine A110 and A110 GT4   2019 Alpine A110 was unveiled in three iterations, a track-only racer called GT4 and two road-legal models, Pure and Légende. All share a 1.8L turbocharged 4-cylinder netting 270 and 252 horses respectively.  7:43 #7 2019 Renault EZ Ultimo  The most recent representation of Renault’s vision of the future was depicted in the trio of concepts based on the home platform, all of which are fully autonomous and electric. The most impressive one is undoubtedly the EZ-Ultimo.  8:54 #8 2019 Renault Zoe  Renault Zoe is the bestselling European electric car on the market, that fits the demand for compact urban commuters, that can squeeze through narrow streets and at the same time gives access to the no pollution zones.

title: RENAULT - Evolution From 1898-2018
description: RENAULT - Evolution From 1898-2018 Groupe Renault is a French multinational automobile manufacturer established in 1899. The company produces a range of cars and vans, and in the past has manufactured trucks, tractors, tanks, buses/coaches and autorail vehicles. According to the Organisation Internationale des Constructeurs d'Automobiles, in 2016 Renault was the ninth biggest automaker in the world by production volume. The Renault–Nissan–Mitsubishi Alliance is the fourth-largest automotive group. Headquartered in Boulogne-Billancourt, near Paris, the Renault group is made up of the namesake Renault marque and subsidiaries, Alpine, Automobile Dacia from Romania, Renault Samsung Motors from South Korea, and AvtoVAZ from Russia. Renault has a 43.4% controlling stake in Nissan of Japan, and a 1.55% stake in Daimler AG of Germany (since 2012, Renault manufactures engines for the Daimler's Mercedes A-Class and B-Class cars). Renault also owns subsidiaries RCI Banque (automotive financing), Renault Retail Group (automotive distribution) and Motrio (automotive parts). Renault has various joint ventures, including Oyak-Renault (Turkey), Renault Pars (Iran). Carlos Ghosn is the current chairman and CEO. The French government owns a 15% share of Renault. title: Renault Clio - Prova su Strada
description: Abbiamo provato su strada la Renault Clio, una delle macchine più vendute in Italia. E abbiamo deciso di provarla in una versione un po' speciale, firmata Moschino!  Entrata in commercio nel lontano 1990, la Renault Clio ha cambiato pelle quattro volte per assecondare i gusti del mercato, e ad ogni edizione ha sempre riscontrato un ottimo successo di vendite.   L’ultima serie della Renault Clio si è posta come punto di riferimento del segmento B sia per il design fluido degli esterni, che per la qualità degli interni. In Italia, la Renault Clio è la seconda berlina più venduta dopo la Fiat Panda.
